title: Latest Buildings (Points) in Haiti, GeoFabrik, February 9, 2010
name: Latest Buildings (Points) in Haiti, GeoFabrik, February 9, 2010
description: These are the latest buildings in Haiti (points) from GeoFabriks Open Street Map extracts. This data was updated on February 9, 2010. These points were generated by downloading a csv from the original shapefile, which was uploaded into Geocommons on February 9, 2010. The csv was saved and then re-uploaded into Geocommons to get points using the latitude/longitude attributes.
